---
---

<section class="hero section" id="hero" aria-label="Главная секция">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-inner">

      <div class="hero-badge animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay:0.05s">
        <span class="status-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="text-mono" style="font-size:var(--text-xs);color:var(--c-text-secondary)">Открыт к предложениям</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="hero-name animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay:0.1s">
        Константин<br />Попов
      </h1>

      <p class="hero-title animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay:0.18s">
        Senior Project Manager
      </p>

      <p class="hero-tagline animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay:0.24s">
        Автоматизация&nbsp;•&nbsp;Внедрения&nbsp;•&nbsp;Интеграции&nbsp;•&nbsp;Производственные&nbsp;системы
      </p>

      <p class="hero-description animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay:0.32s">
        Управляю сложными проектами автоматизации и внедрения на производственных предприятиях. 
        6+ лет опыта, проекты до 30+ млн ₽, реализация в РФ, РБ и ОАЭ.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-actions animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay:0.4s">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn--primary">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path></svg>
          Связаться
        </a>
        <a href="#projects" class="btn btn--outline">
          Посмотреть проекты
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-geo animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay:0.46s">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/><path d="M12 2a8 8 0 0 0-8 8c0 5.25 8 14 8 14s8-8.75 8-14a8 8 0 0 0-8-8z"/></svg>
        <span>РФ / РБ / ОАЭ</span>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="hero-decoration" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="deco-grid"></div>
      <div class="deco-circle"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: clamp(500px, 80vh, 800px);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding-top: clamp(3rem, 8vh, 6rem);
    padding-bottom: clamp(3rem, 8vh, 6rem);
  }

  .hero .container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: var(--c-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    border-radius: 100px;
    padding: 0.35rem 0.85rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
  }

  .status-dot {
    width: 7px;
    height: 7px;
    background: var(--c-success);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: pulse-dot 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .hero-name {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 7vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: var(--c-text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: clamp(var(--text-sm), 2vw, var(--text-base));
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--c-accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    font-size: clamp(var(--text-sm), 2.5vw, var(--text-lg));
    color: var(--c-text-secondary);
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .hero-description {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--c-text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-geo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--c-text-muted);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  /* Decoration */
  .hero-decoration {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    width: 50%;
    height: 100%;
    pointer-events: none;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .deco-grid {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(var(--c-border) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, var(--c-border) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 48px 48px;
    mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 100% at 80% 50%, black 20%, transparent 70%);
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .deco-circle {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    right: -5%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: clamp(200px, 35vw, 420px);
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    border: 1px solid var(--c-border);
    border-radius: 50%;
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 40px rgba(59,130,246,0.02),
      0 0 0 80px rgba(59,130,246,0.015);
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .hero-decoration { width: 100%; opacity: 0.3; }
    .hero-inner { max-width: 100%; }
  }
</style>
